WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.920 --> 00:00:03.360
Well, we scraped through there folks,

2
00:00:04.280 --> 00:00:07.200
I knew we'd do it eventually,
 but we cost the DCI a night's sleep.

3
00:00:08.160 --> 00:00:11.000
Looks like you owe the DCI a few cakes
 when she's back in work.

4
00:00:11.760 --> 00:00:13.200
Job's not done, though.

5
00:00:13.200 --> 00:00:15.480
If the DCI can get caught out
so can anyone.

6
00:00:16.000 --> 00:00:19.920
So make sure you pass on all the
 information and advice you've picked up today.

7
00:00:19.920 --> 00:00:23.760
Make sure you, your friends
 and your family are protected online.

8
00:00:24.600 --> 00:00:26.960
Stay safe and well done.

